                p
                p(style='margin-block: 0.5em 0; text-align: justify; text-justify: inter-word;color:#FF0000;')
                reminder Reminder:
                p(style='margin-block-end: 0; ')
                span2 This session will assess the performance of the explainability tools for rejection face verification decisions.
                p(style='margin-block-end: 0; ')
